---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-rule-strong py-10 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-copper"></span>
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-bone-mute">
        Straw Dogs LLC / {year}
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="display italic text-sm text-bone-soft" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 14;">
      Story is a technology. Not a talent.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
